üßπ 9Ô∏è‚É£ Undo / Fix
git restore file.c          # undo change
git restore --staged file.c # unstage
git reset --hard HEAD       # DANGER

üö´ üîí 1Ô∏è‚É£0Ô∏è‚É£ Ignore
